data.description: Step into this stunning 5 bedroom, 4.5 bathroom home located in the desirable Bulverde Village neighborhood, perfectly positioned north on 281. Nestled on a beautiful corner lot, this residence is an entertainer's dream with an open floor plan and multiple living areas. The welcoming entryway leads to an office space and both formal living and dining areas. The heart of the home features a living and kitchen combo with a lofty ceiling and cozy fireplace, enhancing the open feel. The kitchen is equipped with modern stainless steel appliances, 42 inch cabinets, a breakfast nook, and a chic coffee bar area. The first floor grand primary suite boasts a large en suite with a garden tub, perfect for unwinding. Upstairs, a loft provides additional living space, complemented by spacious bedrooms, including a secondary primary suite.  Outside, the expansive backyard features a covered patio and an extended concrete patio surrounded by ample grassy area, ideal for outdoor enjoyment. Solar panels for energy efficiency complete the outside.  This home combines luxury with practical living in a prime location.
